### HTTP Request

`POST <%= current_page.data.api_url %>/videos/:id/flag`

<aside class="warning">
An X-Apikey header containing a valid API key is required to access this endpoint.
</aside>

### Query Parameters

Parameter    | Default | Description
---------    | ------- | -----------
flag[reason] |         | inappropriate or copyright

### Error Responses

Code | Message
---- | -------
